{"tid":787718,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"NASA買票就進得去?   但中國人不行","createTime":"2018-08-21T02:01:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T04:46:13.000Z","uid":184679,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c78ba8dc7bb0c5442968131498d9dbdc038f6fc7","tid":787718,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T02:01:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/iWGwEUBAVCoOQDvfcdjmQA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/61df11418842700a81aa8eef2e8ff07e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FiWGwEUBAVCoOQDvfcdjmQA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F61df11418842700a81aa8eef2e8ff07e&h=93f327a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲蔡英文在太空人帶領下參訪NASA。（圖／中央社）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總統蔡英文結束同慶之旅友邦出訪行程，20日回程過境休士頓時參訪NASA詹森太空中心，成為首位參訪該機構的台灣總統。此舉動讓中國官媒《環球時報》引述網友批評，指稱只要買票人人都能進去，何來「突破」？不過該說法也被ptt鄉民搬出法條打臉，NASA明訂「中國人」不得進入參觀。<br />\n<br />\n針對蔡英文參訪NASA，中國官媒《環球網》記者撰文表示，安排蔡英文參訪NASA是美國一貫的伎倆、打「擦邊球」。報導指出，由於《台灣旅行法》通過，美方為了提升美台官方交流層級，但又不想過於刺激中國，而NASA是一個「不太敏感的官方機構」，這才安排此行，是一種「漸進式的突破」。<br />\n<br />\n《環球網》報導也引述部分網友說法，「不知道有什麼好高興的，又是一個買票可以進去的聯邦機構」，質疑人人都進得去，何來「突破」？不過這個說法也馬上ptt鄉民翻出法條打臉，根據2011年4月美國國會訂立的「中國人禁令」，除非有綠卡，否則中國人是無法入內參觀的。<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文此行來到NASA太空中心，不但參訪了一般遊客的參觀區，更在美方安排下，由太空人芬克（Michael Fincke）帶領進入主控室並簡報，不論從什麼角度看，確實都是一大突破。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/UGdWdqpT29lE5SsvgcA7OQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/315c9523c4a254e808f223c7add8e264\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FUGdWdqpT29lE5SsvgcA7OQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F315c9523c4a254e808f223c7add8e264&h=7182ba2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲蔡英文進到NASA主控室，是台灣總統首例。（圖／中央社）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/nasa%E8%B2%B7%E7%A5%A8%E5%B0%B1%E9%80%B2%E5%BE%97%E5%8E%BB-%E4%BD%86%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8D%E8%A1%8C-025506373.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2Fnasa%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E9%2580%25B2%25E5%25BE%2597%25E5%258E%25BB-%25E4%25BD%2586%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25A1%258C-025506373.html&d=QmOEhSBQvQAZ%2Bsr1emArUqMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=d564c8f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/nasa%E8%B2%B7%E7%A5%A8%E5%B0%B1%E9%80%B2%E5%BE%97%E5%8E%BB-%E4%BD%86%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8D%E8%A1%8C-025506373.html</a>"},{"pid":"11d63721646869f5890825af08aefefa8bc74f3f","tid":787718,"uid":37661,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T02:05:06.000Z","msg":"雜種個女都係中国人，一樣可以參觀呀。<br />\n<br />\n有綠卡唔可以做中国人咩？"},{"pid":"1a34570fec38a720d86f46b94a4214f0a823ee9e","tid":787718,"uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T02:05:21.000Z","msg":"事實上，NASA於二○一三年時，就曾因拒絕中國科學家出席開普勒天文望遠鏡項目的國際學術會議而引起軒然大波。當時NASA表示，是根據「聯邦反間諜法」中「NASA不可在旗下設施內接待任何中華人民共和國國民」等內容，拒絕中國科學家的申請；另在「二○一二年度綜合撥款法案」中，也通過了「NASA排華條款」，禁止NASA以其資金接待中國官方訪客，NASA科學家也不得與中國企業有關聯的中國公民合作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/focus/paper/1226092\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffocus%2Fpaper%2F1226092&d=QmOEhSBQvQAZ%2Bsr1emArUqMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=6cc5b526\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffocus%2Fpaper%2F1226092&h=725dab3a\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/focus/paper/1226092</a>"},{"pid":"05e03c5746eb0a3e21cee67aecc3ad197ce06538","tid":787718,"uid":39628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T02:08:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支那狗"},{"p